{"id": "ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 26, "displayName": {"text": "Yumee Katsu - Castro Valley", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxd2MyZENORjlFZW00MVdrcERNR1JRZGtFM2MxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Food was much better than expected.  I had the Katsu assortment which included shrimp and fried cheese...came with 3 dipping sauce all very good.  My spouse had the fried fish and it was good also...not greasy 😋 we also tried the rice cake...the sauce was amazing spicy but not too spicy.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Food was much better than expected.  I had the Katsu assortment which included shrimp and fried cheese...came with 3 dipping sauce all very good.  My spouse had the fried fish and it was good also...not greasy 😋 we also tried the rice cake...the sauce was amazing spicy but not too spicy.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jerie Fletcher", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108727943696052525792/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeC37x_RvppLTz6EHjnmGoZ0y_9AfUZkijSY66uNN1Jq0u_rU2=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T23:08:37.603886099Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxd2MyZENORjlFZW00MVdrcERNR1JRZGtFM2MxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxd2MyZENORjlFZW00MVdrcERNR1JRZGtFM2MxRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f93d104f231e9:0xea729a8e4ad8c4f1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1UmFWbEJiRlJsTUZKcFZIRmFVMWM1ZERkc2IxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Absolutely one of our favorite katsu places. Been going to their Dublin location for a while. Super happy they opened one now in Castro Valley that is closer to us.\n\nFood is so delicious. I tried the combo and curry.\nThe pork curry is amazing and I have been always coming back for this dish.\n\nHighly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Absolutely one of our favorite katsu places. Been going to their Dublin location for a while. Super happy they opened one now in Castro Valley that is closer to us.\n\nFood is so delicious. I tried the combo and curry.\nThe pork curry is amazing and I have been always coming back for this dish.\n\nHighly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sia Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115849938470327197083/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI29iEHZU8becXGSW6v81ezoVO7jZx153jCoKfs5xFkuEUbUPI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-15T05:15:47.465081555Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1UmFWbEJiRlJsTUZKcFZIRmFVMWM1ZERkc2IxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1UmFWbEJiRlJsTUZKcFZIRmFVMWM1ZERkc2IxRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f93d104f231e9:0xea729a8e4ad8c4f1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkUFRsWlVRa2w1U1ZrdFp6SnVSRGRwT0c5V1NWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Delicious food. Fast attentive service. Family friendly atmosphere and clean modern decor.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Delicious food. Fast attentive service. Family friendly atmosphere and clean modern decor.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Excel Ang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114007836250107119037/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2xQzqlrN8JawIz-DfT0YRjGzP42obN0Btp9DOIJ26fK-nXGZvEg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T04:04:02.017245483Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkUFRsWlVRa2w1U1ZrdFp6SnVSRGRwT0c5V1NWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkUFRsWlVRa2w1U1ZrdFp6SnVSRGRwT0c5V1NWRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f93d104f231e9:0xea729a8e4ad8c4f1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psM2EyWjVPVUZNUjB0R2RHVXlUMkpIUVROUlNHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The food is really good. It fills a niche that doesn't exist in Castro Valley.\n\nI think the Banchan is a little lacking, but the flavor is there. One of our orders we added a small udon and it was basically added to the small soup. You can see the size comparison in the photos.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The food is really good. It fills a niche that doesn't exist in Castro Valley.\n\nI think the Banchan is a little lacking, but the flavor is there. One of our orders we added a small udon and it was basically added to the small soup. You can see the size comparison in the photos.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kyle Pace", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102174114218519255627/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV24m_RBL6ZTM5Geud4k7IIPj3gPhkWX_O2N0kOzKneoDIrKtTZBQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-21T02:14:10.866796691Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psM2EyWjVPVUZNUjB0R2RHVXlUMkpIUVROUlNHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psM2EyWjVPVUZNUjB0R2RHVXlUMkpIUVROUlNHYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f93d104f231e9:0xea729a8e4ad8c4f1"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OMVFqRnBNa2x6WVhaMVluVTRTbWg1ZG1zemNrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Katsu is fried well and doesn’t eat oily or greasy. I will note that the portion sizes for sides and rice seem off, and they charge extra for sauce (1 is included, not enough).\n\nOverall I am happy with the addition to the Castro valley food option", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Katsu is fried well and doesn’t eat oily or greasy. I will note that the portion sizes for sides and rice seem off, and they charge extra for sauce (1 is included, not enough).\n\nOverall I am happy with the addition to the Castro valley food option", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "A K", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117450790756521519325/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNy_EWt3MoFgYzvZeEznSZtzt-5QKSxmDK1T3vi3bSmRkMU9uN4A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-30T03:46:57.329224127Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OMVFqRnBNa2x6WVhaMVluVTRTbWg1ZG1zemNrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OMVFqRnBNa2x6WVhaMVluVTRTbWg1ZG1zemNrRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f93d104f231e9:0xea729a8e4ad8c4f1"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ6THyBNGTj4AR8cTYSo6acuo/photos/AWCwydgluGWPkD9sqvJ3MP-XRkI3vyMO4aS74EeWUBSizFaWWaryJfH-9ZpZRImUn_td5C9PZLpOo5IKlwpPUVB3cESEJp19hlf8_FE80tzNWaGKs7tIv1KD3pGNIlYk1BrCf_FlrAopNDrI6Mk9KhZaUCaGieEhXikIFxdrjWuTaXEpLcKzoD3cexOBPU1RgSglELjaB-TNI0aZfWQwrTCwy0bdQu4CCVFhKKA8YfNCjViyDAH1JG0v19YagRyZO1EOCh-SQtN28aqo0bQ70jgdcXzhJN4mG3lnK9eX3mLMfzg7bdNJ8EexmpBdMhi5bRI6O950mlBc5jupx_hnRYkdzY8WgdE-1Bdh6a6-67WSMprkkde7SpSOeUN_JpRZc-0L2-S2eVDug2LWhjUNe7J7A4Ko_QykqE66WLbZ3e_YCA_KYPpfDAIn0hPsQ4rHhE1O", "widthPx": 4000, "heightPx": 3000, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Yumee Katsu - Castro Valley", "uri